# calculate.website — Cloudflare Pages redirects
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NOTE: Wildcard rules like /es/* were removed because Cloudflare evaluates
# _redirects BEFORE checking static files, so /es/* was catching /es/ even
# though /es/index.html exists — causing language switching to silently loop
# back to the English homepage.
#
# Missing translated calculator pages now return 404 instead of silently
# falling back to EN. This is the correct behavior: it avoids confusing users
# into thinking they're reading a translated page when they're not.
#
# When a calculator page is translated, add it to the correct language folder.
# No redirects needed once the file exists.
